---
layout: layout.njk
title: Services
description: "Askia coaching services to land top tech roles."
---
<section class="hero">
  <div class="container hero-grid">
    <div>
      <p class="hero-eyebrow">Services</p>
      <h1 class="hero-title section-title-glow">{{ services.hero.title }}</h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">{{ services.hero.subtitle }}</p>
      <div class="hero-cta">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="{{ services.hero.ctaLink }}">{{ services.hero.ctaLabel }}</a>
        <span class="hero-proof">⏱ Typical turnaround 7–14 days · Coaching timelines 2–6 weeks</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="service-hero-orbit">
      <div class="orbit-card">
        <strong>Outcomes you can feel</strong>
        <p>Clear positioning, real interview momentum, and an offer strategy you can execute.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="orbit-ring"></div>
      <div class="orbit-dot"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container service-spectrum">
    <div class="spectrum-header">
      <p class="hero-eyebrow">Service Spectrum</p>
      <h2 class="section-title section-title-glow">Pick your lane. Stack your advantage.</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">Each offer is designed as a module. Start with precision, then layer coaching when momentum hits.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="spectrum-grid">
      {% for tier in services.tiers %}
        <article class="spectrum-card{% if tier.tag == 'Most Popular' %} is-featured{% endif %}">
          <div class="spectrum-top">
            <span class="spectrum-tag">{{ tier.tag }}</span>
            <h3>{{ tier.title }}</h3>
            <p>{{ tier.body }}</p>
          </div>
          <div class="spectrum-meta">
            <span>{{ tier.ideal }}</span>
            <span>{{ tier.turnaround }}</span>
          </div>
          <ul>
            {% for bullet in tier.bullets %}
              <li>{{ bullet }}</li>
            {% endfor %}
          </ul>
        </article>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container service-composer">
    <div class="composer-copy">
      <p class="hero-eyebrow">Build Your Stack</p>
      <h2 class="section-title section-title-glow">Mix. Match. Move faster.</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">Most clients start with Brand refresh, then layer coaching once interviews hit. We’ll help you choose the fastest path.</p>
      <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="{{ services.cta.ctaLink }}">Get a recommendation</a>
    </div>
    <div class="composer-tiles">
      <div class="composer-tile">Resume Upgrade</div>
      <div class="composer-tile">LinkedIn Signal</div>
      <div class="composer-tile">Cover Letter</div>
      <div class="composer-tile">Clarity Coaching</div>
      <div class="composer-tile">Interview Practice</div>
      <div class="composer-tile">Negotiation</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container service-journey">
    <div>
      <h2 class="section-title section-title-glow">How we move you from "maybe" to offers</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">A clear, repeatable journey that turns experience into market‑ready positioning.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="journey-steps">
      <div class="journey-step">
        <span>01</span>
        <h4>Signal</h4>
        <p>Build a brand story recruiters instantly recognize.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="journey-step">
        <span>02</span>
        <h4>Momentum</h4>
        <p>Turn strategy into interviews with targeted outreach.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="journey-step">
        <span>03</span>
        <h4>Conversion</h4>
        <p>Interview execution + negotiation to secure top offers.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container faq-stage">
    <div class="faq-header">
      <h2 class="section-title section-title-glow">{{ services.faq.title }}</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">Short, clear answers to the questions we hear most before someone books.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-grid">
      {% for item in services.faq.items %}
        <details class="faq-card">
          <summary>{{ item.question }}</summary>
          <p>{{ item.answer }}</p>
        </details>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container cta-band">
    <div>
      <h2 class="section-title">{{ services.cta.title }}</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">{{ services.cta.body }}</p>
    </div>
    <a class="btn btn-primary" href="{{ services.cta.ctaLink }}">{{ services.cta.ctaLabel }}</a>
  </div>
</section>
